# ðŸ”¸ Graphql Queries

GraphQl queries get data (read data) - without specification ( without parameters )  
_Example: getting all the products from database_

## ðŸ”¹ Define a Query Schema

``` graphql
#Define a query schema
type Query {
    Query:
     # <data-property-name>: <type>
     products: [Product]
}

```

## ðŸ”¹ Execute a Query

``` graphql
#Describe/compose a query ( describing with "<code class='preserveHtml' >query"</code> operation )
query {
  #<property-name> {
   # <sub-property-name>
   # <sub-property-name>
   # ...
  #}
  products {
      id
      title
      description
      price
  }
}
#Describe/compose a query ( without describing with "query" operation - by default )
{
  #<property-name> {
   # <sub-property-name>
   # <sub-property-name>
   # ...
  #}
  products {
      id
      title
      description
      price
  }
}

```

